Cruz Beckham, 17, opted for a bold look as he stepped out with his dad, David Beckham, 47, at the Dior Homme show at Paris Fashion Week.David’s youngest son showed off his fashion credentials in a bright green blazer over a white vest top paired with some flared, black trousers.Cruz accessorized with a gold necklace shaped like a cannabis plant layered on top of two chains.He looked the spitting image of David as he sported a hairstyle similar to his dad’s infamous blonde highlights. 